{
  "stem": "7781.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was kind of-- I-- I had a happy childhood, regardless of all the other, you know, things that we faced, being-- as a Jewish child.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a close-knit family, and we-- I didn't experience any, you know, like, I am being deprived of anything.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- was enough food in the house, and we lived in two big rooms.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- and the winter, you know, we didn't know anything else.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I think I had a happy childhood.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mom was a very nice person.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She-- she worked hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She never complained.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and she had to prepare food, she had a full-time job, just to feed nine people every day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You had breakfast and lunch and-- and, you know, and supper, and then for the holidays-- but she-- she never complained, because she had the means, she had-- we had the money to buy the food, compared to other people that problem-- had problems feeding themselves.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in this regard, we were-- we were good off.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, because we didn't experience any hunger, or we didn't get all the food that we wanted to eat during the week, but there was no hunger.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was enough food to eat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was enough bread and butter and herring.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was no, let's say, cold cuts, or other stuff, you know, but basically, there was always-- there-- there was no problem with food.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were kind of always busy, the family, my father had to shop in the same building, and I could always go and do something, and I was never-- I was never bored.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they used to send you down after school to work in the shop?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was voluntary.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That-- I was not-- I was not forced to.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
